rows.label: bf11560100_0010
rows.name: Hey, partner. First time we've met.

rows.label: bf11560100_0020
rows.name: Metsu...

rows.label: bf11560100_0030
rows.name: So that's the Heaven's Holy Grail, Metsu...

rows.label: bf11560100_0040
rows.name: His presence is overwhelming...

rows.label: bf11560100_0045
rows.name: As a fellow Blade, I even feel fear.

rows.label: bf11560100_0050
rows.name: Same here.

rows.label: bf11560100_0060
rows.name:
This is a pretty different approach for you.
What's your goal?

rows.label: bf11560100_0070
rows.name:
If this is some kind of game,
your taste is too awful.

rows.label: bf11560100_0080
rows.name: I got bored of it.

rows.label: bf11560100_0090
rows.name: ...Bored?

rows.label: bf11560100_0100
rows.name: It's boring just sinking stuff with Siren.

rows.label: bf11560100_0110
rows.name:
I felt like watching the humans dance to their deaths,
surrounded by the flames of hell.

rows.label: bf11560100_0120
rows.name: What do you mean?

rows.label: bf11560100_0130
rows.name: Look over there.

rows.label: bf11560100_0140
rows.name:
I know very well what kind of thing
this Divine Beast is.

rows.label: bf11560100_0150
rows.name:
So I thought, hey, maybe it'd be fun
to see it reveal its true form.

rows.label: bf11560100_0160
rows.name: You bastard... you don't mean...

rows.label: bf11560100_0170
rows.name: Every single one of the Devices I command...

rows.label: bf11560100_0180
rows.name:
...has ether energy stored up
that rivals a massive Divine Beast.

rows.label: bf11560100_0190
rows.name:
What if 10000 of those Devices attached to the Iiran
Core and poured all that energy in at the same time?

rows.label: bf11560100_0200
rows.name:
It might be so amazing you won't
even have time to dance.

rows.label: bf11560100_0210
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]Guh!

rows.label: bf11560100_0220
rows.name: You want to stop me, right?

rows.label: bf11560100_0225
rows.name: Fine. I'll let you stop me.

rows.label: bf11560100_0230
rows.name: Come on. Bring it.
